  "text": "{\\fad(150,150)}Quasi!"
 },
 {
  "i": 173,
  "style": "Note",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "{\\fad(150,150)}Rump"
 },
 {
  "i": 174,
  "style": "Thoughts",
  "name": "Absalom",
  "text": "What's with his strength?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 175,
  "style": "Thoughts",
  "name": "Absalom",
  "text": "Is he really just an underling?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 176,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "{\\fad(150,150)}Queue!"
 },
 {
  "i": 177,
  "style": "Note",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "{\\fad(150,150)}Tail"
 },
 {
  "i": 178,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "{\\fad(150,150)}Cuisseau!"
 },
 {
  "i": 179,
  "style": "Note",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "{\\fad(150,150)}Thigh"
 },
 {
  "i": 180,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "{\\fad(150,150)}Jarret!"
 },
 {
  "i": 181,
  "style": "Note",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "{\\fad(150,150)}Shin"
 },
 {
  "i": 182,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "Why is she unconscious?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 183,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "You better not have gotten violent with her!"
 },
 {
  "i": 184,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "What marriage?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 185,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "Look at my eyes! I'll kick the hell out of you and make a croquette with your remains!"
 },
 {
  "i": 186,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Absalom",
  "text": "Damn! I gotta avoid him!"
 },
 {
  "i": 187,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Absalom",
  "text": "{\\fad(150,150)}Skating..."
 },
 {
  "i": 188,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "{\\fad(150,150)}Usopp's Special Salt Ball..."
 },
 {
  "i": 189,
  "style": "Thoughts",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "There he is!"
 },
 {
  "i": 190,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Absalom",
  "text": "What?! It's salty!"
 },
 {
  "i": 191,
  "style": "Note",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "{\\fad(150,150)}Veal Shot"
 },
 {
  "i": 192,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "{\\fad(150,150)}Veau Shot!"
 },
 {
  "i": 193,
  "style": "Thoughts",
  "name": "Absalom",
  "text": "Impossible..."
 },
 {
  "i": 194,
  "style": "Thoughts",
  "name": "Absalom",
  "text": "This guy doesn't even have a bounty..."
 },
 {
  "i": 195,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "You say you're irritated...?"
 },
 {
  "i": 196,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "That's nothing compared to me..."
 },
 {
  "i": 197,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "My body is exploding with rage!"
 },
 {
  "i": 198,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Zombie",
  "text": "It is!"
 },
 {
  "i": 199,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "And there's one more unfortunate thing..."
 },
 {
  "i": 200,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "You and I have..."
 },
 {
  "i": 201,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "A connection!"
 },
 {
  "i": 202,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Zombie",
  "text": "A-Absalom-sama..."
 },
 {
  "i": 203,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Absalom",
  "text": "You and I have a connection?"
 },
 {
  "i": 204,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "That's right, you're the man who stole my dream."
 },
 {
  "i": 205,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Absalom",
  "text": "I don't remember you."
 },
 {
  "i": 206,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Absalom",
  "text": "It must be some kind of misunderstanding."
 },
 {
  "i": 207,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Absalom",
  "text": "Today is the first time..."
 },
 {
  "i": 208,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Absalom",
  "text": "I've ever met with you."
 },
 {
  "i": 209,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Absalom",
  "text": "I'll blow you away!"
 },
 {
  "i": 210,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Absalom",
  "text": "With these Hands of the Dead!"
 },
 {
  "i": 211,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "Take them off."
 },
 {
  "i": 212,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "I told you to take off those bazookas attached to your arms."
 },
 {
  "i": 213,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "Don't you get it?"
 },
 {
  "i": 214,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "If Nami-san gets hurt because of your mindless attack, you won't appear very alive when I finish with you."
 },
 {
  "i": 215,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Absalom",
  "text": "He knows nothing..."
 },
 {
  "i": 216,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "I told you to..."
 },
 {
  "i": 217,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "Take them off!"
 },
 {
  "i": 218,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Zombie",
  "text": "What?! A bazooka suddenly appeared!"
 },
 {
  "i": 219,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "That's how it is, right?"
 },
 {
  "i": 220,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "That's a very clever attack."
 },
 {
  "i": 221,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "You make your body invisible, and anything that comes in contact with your body invisible."
 },
 {
  "i": 222,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "That's your ability..."
 },
 {
  "i": 223,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "The Transparent Fruit's invisible man."
 },
 {
  "i": 224,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "I know everything you're capable of!"
 },
 {
  "i": 225,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Absalom",
  "text": "How is that possible...?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 226,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Absalom",
  "text": "Who are you...?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 227,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Zombie",
  "text": "Has that man met Absalom-sama before?"
 },
 {
  "i": 228,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Zombie",
  "text": "Why does he know everything about his abilities?"
 },
 {
  "i": 229,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "When I was a kid, I saw a large picture book about the devil fruit."
 },
 {
  "i": 230,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "At first, I wasn't interested in all those rumors about sea curses, but..."
 },
 {
  "i": 231,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "while flipping through it, I came across a single item that caught my eye."
 },
 {
  "i": 232,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "If I happened to find that ability..."
 },
 {
  "i": 233,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "even if I was to become cursed, I'd gladly eat it!"
 },
 {
  "i": 234,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "But two of the same fruit don't exist in this world."
 },
 {
  "i": 235,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "If by any chance, I ran into the user of that fruit, my dream would collapse!"
 },
 {
  "i": 236,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "You get it now?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 237,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "I wished to become the invisible man!"
 },
 {
  "i": 238,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "That's why, the moment you ate the\\NTransparent Fruit, you crushed my dream!"
 },
 {
  "i": 239,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Zombie",
  "text": "He's right!"
 },
 {
  "i": 240,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "I wanted my dream to come true!"
 },
 {
  "i": 241,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "If so, with that ability I'd enter the..."
 },
 {
  "i": 242,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "women's bath!"
 },
 {
  "i": 243,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "No, I'd do something honorable in the..."
 },
 {
  "i": 244,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "women's bath!"
 },
 {
  "i": 245,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "No, I'd definitely help the people in the..."
 },
 {
  "i": 246,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "women's bath!"
 },
 {
  "i": 247,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Zombie",
  "text": "He wants nothing but to peek into the women's bath!"
 },
 {
  "i": 248,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "Shut up!"
 },
 {
  "i": 249,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "But thanks to many years of simulation, I know everything you can see-"
 },
 {
  "i": 250,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "No, everything you can do with that ability!"
 },
 {
  "i": 251,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "And if we add that you put Nami-san in danger, that means I'll definitely never forgive you!"
 },
 {
  "i": 252,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "Women's ba-"
 },
 {
  "i": 253,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "No! You better be ready to die!"
 },
 {
  "i": 254,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Absalom",
  "text": "What're you thinking?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 255,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Absalom",
  "text": "What a ridiculous connection!"
 },
 {
  "i": 256,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Absalom",
  "text": "That's the most stupid thing I've ever heard!"
 },
 {
  "i": 257,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Absalom",
  "text": "You're a...!"
 },
 {
  "i": 258,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Absalom",
  "text": "freaking pervert!"
 },
 {
  "i": 259,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "I don't want to...!"
 },
 {
  "i": 260,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "Hear that from you!"
 },
 {
  "i": 261,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Zombie",
  "text": "He's right!"
 },
 {
  "i": 262,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Zombie",
  "text": "But they're the same!"
 },
 {
  "i": 263,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Absalom",
  "text": "Very well!"
 },
 {
  "i": 264,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Absalom",
  "text": "I'll return your connection, your rage, everything back to you!"
 },
 {
  "i": 265,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Absalom",
  "text": "Not only do I have a lion's jaw...!"
 },
 {
  "i": 266,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Absalom",
  "text": "Elephant skin...!"
 },
 {
  "i": 267,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Absalom",
  "text": "Three hundred kilograms of condensed bear and gorilla muscle!"
 },
 {
  "i": 268,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Absalom",
  "text": "Implant after implant, Dr. Hogback kept working on me until I obtained the ultimate masterpiece body!"
 },
 {
  "i": 269,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Absalom",
  "text": "The Transparent Fruit is nothing but an bonus."
 },
 {
  "i": 270,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Absalom",
  "text": "It doesn't even compare to the terrible strength I have!"
 },
 {
  "i": 271,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Absalom",
  "text": "Do you understand now?"
 },
 {
  "i": 272,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "But..."
 },
 {
  "i": 273,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "You still peeked on her!"
 },
 {
  "i": 274,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Zombie",
  "text": "It is true!"
 },
 {
  "i": 275,
  "style": "Thoughts",
  "name": "Absalom",
  "text": "If it had been an ordinary kick, his leg would've been destroyed..."
 },
 {
  "i": 276,
  "style": "Thoughts",
  "name": "Absalom",
  "text": "It's just as if my body was a regular human body to him."
 },
 {
  "i": 277,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Absalom",
  "text": "But I'll have the last laugh!"
 },
 {
  "i": 278,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Absalom",
  "text": "You lost the ability you wished for and now even the woman you intend to protect will be my bride!"
 },
 {
  "i": 279,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Absalom",
  "text": "You've no chance to beat me in this state!"
 },
 {
  "i": 280,
  "style": "Flashbacks",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Back then, Nami disappeared along with him and we couldn't follow him!"
 },
 {
  "i": 281,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "You want to hide Nami-san, don't you?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 282,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "Over my dead body!"
 },
 {
  "i": 283,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Absalom",
  "text": "It's useless!"
 },
 {
  "i": 284,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Absalom",
  "text": "I'll show you the power of the beast man!"
 },
 {
  "i": 285,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Absalom",
  "text": "So you intend to sacrifice yourself for that woman?"
 },
 {
  "i": 286,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Absalom",
  "text": "Protect her then!"
 },
 {
  "i": 287,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Absalom",
  "text": "If you can!"
 },
 {
  "i": 288,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Absalom",
  "text": "{\\fad(150,150)}Beast Man's Hands!"
 },
 {
  "i": 289,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Absalom",
  "text": "{\\fad(150,150)}Beast Man's Legs!"
 },
 {
  "i": 290,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Absalom",
  "text": "Don't let go of her!"
 },
 {
  "i": 291,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "Sorry... Nami-san..."
 },
 {
  "i": 292,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Absalom",
  "text": "You let her go?"
 },
 {
  "i": 293,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Absalom",
  "text": "So you value your life over hers after all!"
 },
 {
  "i": 294,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "Sorry..."
 },
 {
  "i": 295,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "I don't wanna stain that snow white dress..."
 },
 {
  "i": 296,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "Damn... you just hide and sneak, you invisible man..."
 },
 {
  "i": 297,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "I don't give a damn about that dream anymore..."
 },
 {
  "i": 298,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "I no longer... care about being an invisible man!"
 },
 {
  "i": 299,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "I'll peek on my own!"
 },
 {
  "i": 300,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Zombie",
  "text": "You still wanna peek?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 301,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Absalom",
  "text": "Let go of me, bastard!"
 },
 {
  "i": 302,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Absalom",
  "text": "Let go!"
 },
 {
  "i": 303,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "Like I would, you filthy bastard!"
 },
 {
  "i": 304,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "If you're made of many beasts..."
 },
 {
  "i": 305,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "You'll make a fine minced meat!"
 },
 {
  "i": 306,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Absalom",
  "text": "Shut up! Let go of me!"
 },
 {
  "i": 307,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "{\\fad(150,150)}Extra Haché!"
 },
 {
  "i": 308,
  "style": "Note",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "{\\fad(150,150)}Haché: Mincemeat"
 },
 {
  "i": 309,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Zombie",
  "text": "Absalom-sama!"
 },
 {
  "i": 310,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "Women's bath..."
 },
 {
  "i": 311,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "No..."
 },
 {
  "i": 312,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "A beast's bride..."
 },
 {
  "i": 313,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "Ought to be another beast."
 },
 {
  "i": 314,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Perona",
  "text": "He's still following me!"
 },
 {
  "i": 315,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pelona",
  "text": "If it wasn't for him, I'd have already beaten the other pirates!"
 },
 {
  "i": 316,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pelona",
  "text": "Damn Nega-nose!"
 },
 {
  "i": 317,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "He's still following me!"
 },
 {
  "i": 318,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "If it wasn't for him, I'd have already beaten that hollow-hollow woman!"
 },
 {
  "i": 319,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Damn bear zombie!"
 },
 {
  "i": 320,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Kumashi",
  "text": "Wait...!"
 },
 {
  "i": 321,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Stay away!"
 },
 {
  "i": 322,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Wait, hollow-hollow woman!"
 },
 {
  "i": 323,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Perona",
  "text": "Stay away!"
 },
 {
  "i": 324,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Perona",
  "text": "Kumashi, hurry up and stop him!"
 },
 {
  "i": 325,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Kumashi",
  "text": "Wait...!"
 },
 {
  "i": 326,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Kumashi",
  "text": "Don't lay a hand on Perona-sama...!"
 },
 {
  "i": 327,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Too close! Too close!"
 },
 {
  "i": 328,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Kumashi",
  "text": "Perona-sama...!"
 },
 {
  "i": 329,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "What a terrifying power for a stuffed doll!"
